      <title>苹果计划于 9 月 10 日推出新款 iPhone、AirPods 和手表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/when-is-apple-announcing-the-iphone-16-apple-planning-event-on-sept-10-2024</link>
